publish:property.name: Body
publish:property.publish:value: A NetworkProductSpec might be monitored or not. The wording monitored means that the user can’t realise a type of usage if he hasn’t any FixedVolumePackageProd for this type of usage (i.e. without an empty balance). In this case, the attribute isUsageMonitoring is TRUE.
